715671f-a.title: Manhattan: 152nd Street - 7th Avenue
715671f-a.text:
West 152nd Street, west from but not including Seventh Ave., to and
including Macombs Place. Buildings shown are on West 15lst Street,
south side, west from but not including Seventh Ave., to and including
Macombs Place. The two white buildings shown are No's 280-284 West
15lst Street at Ahich are located the Church of the Resurrection,
School and Rectory.
August 24, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
